details.name: Battle Hunger
details.description: Enrages an enemy unit, causing it to be slowed and take damage over time until it kills another unit or the duration ends. Axe gains movement speed for each unit affected with Battle Hunger, half speed from creeps. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Causes Battle Hunger to be an AoE ability, and provides -30% damage output reduction.
